summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 45E, page 119, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Burke's 2nd Addition, Lots 1, 2, 3, 4, 11, 12, 13, 14, Block 21, and Lots 1-9, inclusive, Block 16, Wood Supplement, located south of King St. between alley west of 30th Ave. So. and 32nd Ave. So. as Multiple Residence (RM) Zone.
